    "html": "<div class=\"B1_text_xin\" id=\"cont\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\\\" src=\"https://www.liaotuo.com/uploadfile/2016/1202/20161202023007662.jpg\" style=\"width: 278px; height: 235px;\" /></div>\n<h3>（如发现注音有错误，请您联系我们，便于我们及时纠正，qq：1300659095。<a href=\"/remen/ganen.html\" class=\"keylink\" target=\"_blank\">感恩</a>）</h3>\n<p><span>rú<br />&#13;\n如</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wǒ<br />&#13;\n我</span><span>wén<br />&#13;\n闻</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yì<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>shí<br />&#13;\n时</span><span>fó<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>zhù<br />&#13;\n住</span><span>shě<br />&#13;\n舍</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n卫</span><span>qí<br />&#13;\n祇</span><span>tuó<br />&#13;\n陀</span><span>yuán<br />&#13;\n园</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>jǐ<br />&#13;\n给</span><span>gū<br />&#13;\n孤</span><span>dú<br />&#13;\n独</span><span>jīng<br />&#13;\n精</span><span>shè<br />&#13;\n舍</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shí<br />&#13;\n时</span><span>yǐ<br />&#13;\n已</span><span>shēn<br />&#13;\n深</span><span>yè<br />&#13;\n夜</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yǒu<br />&#13;\n有</span><span>yī<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>tiān<br />&#13;\n天</span><span>shén<br />&#13;\n神</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shū<br />&#13;\n殊</span><span>shèng<br />&#13;\n胜</span><span>guāng<br />&#13;\n光</span><span>míng<br />&#13;\n明</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>biàn<br />&#13;\n遍</span><span>zhào<br />&#13;\n照</span><span>yuán<br />&#13;\n园</span><span>zhōng<br />&#13;\n中</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>lái<br />&#13;\n来</span><span>zhì<br />&#13;\n至</span><span>fó<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>suǒ<br />&#13;\n所</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>gōng<br />&#13;\n恭</span><span>jìng<br />&#13;\n敬</span><span>lǐ<br />&#13;\n礼</span><span>bài<br />&#13;\n拜</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>zhàn<br />&#13;\n站</span><span>lì<br />&#13;\n立</span><span>yī<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>páng<br />&#13;\n旁</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yǐ<br />&#13;\n以</span><span>jì<br />&#13;\n偈</span><span>bái<br />&#13;\n白</span><span>fó<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>yán<br />&#13;\n言</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>zhòng<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>tiān<br />&#13;\n天</span><span>shén<br />&#13;\n神</span><span>yǔ<br />&#13;\n与</span><span>rén<br />&#13;\n人</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>kě<br />&#13;\n渴</span><span>wàng<br />&#13;\n望</span><span>dé<br />&#13;\n得</span><span>lì<br />&#13;\n利</span><span>yì<br />&#13;\n益</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>sī<br />&#13;\n思</span><span>lǜ<br />&#13;\n虑</span><span>qiú<br />&#13;\n求</span><span>xìng<br />&#13;\n幸</span><span>fú<br />&#13;\n福</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>qǐng<br />&#13;\n请</span><span>qiú<br />&#13;\n求</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>shì<br />&#13;\n世</span><span>zūn<br />&#13;\n尊</span><span>rú<br />&#13;\n如</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>dā<br />&#13;\n答</span><span>yán<br />&#13;\n言</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span></p>\n<p><span>wù<br />&#13;\n勿</span><span>jìn<br />&#13;\n近</span><span>yú<br />&#13;\n愚</span><span>chī<br />&#13;\n痴</span><span>rén<br />&#13;\n人</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yìng<br />&#13;\n应</span><span>yǔ<br />&#13;\n与</span><span>zhì<br />&#13;\n智</span><span>zhě<br />&#13;\n者</span><span>jiāo<br />&#13;\n交</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>zūn<br />&#13;\n尊</span><span>jìng<br />&#13;\n敬</span><span>yǒu<br />&#13;\n有</span><span>dé<br />&#13;\n德</span><span>zhě<br />&#13;\n者</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>jū<br />&#13;\n居</span><span>zhù<br />&#13;\n住</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n适</span><span>yí<br />&#13;\n宜</span><span>chù<br />&#13;\n处</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>wǎng<br />&#13;\n往</span><span>xī<br />&#13;\n昔</span><span>yǒu<br />&#13;\n有</span><span>dé<br />&#13;\n德</span><span>xíng<br />&#13;\n行</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>zhì<br />&#13;\n置</span><span>shēn<br />&#13;\n身</span><span>yú<br />&#13;\n于</span><span>zhèng<br />&#13;\n正</span><span>dào<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>duō<br />&#13;\n多</span><span>wén<br />&#13;\n闻</span><span>gōng<br />&#13;\n工</span><span>yì<br />&#13;\n艺</span><span>jīng<br />&#13;\n精</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yán<br />&#13;\n严</span><span>chí<br />&#13;\n持</span><span>zhū<br />&#13;\n诸</span><span>jìn<br />&#13;\n禁</span><span>jiè<br />&#13;\n戒</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>yán<br />&#13;\n言</span><span>tán<br />&#13;\n谈</span><span>yuè<br />&#13;\n悦</span><span>rén<br />&#13;\n人</span><span>xīn<br />&#13;\n心</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>fèng<br />&#13;\n奉</span><span>yǎng<br />&#13;\n养</span><span>fù<br />&#13;\n父</span><span>mǔ<br />&#13;\n母</span><span>qīn<br />&#13;\n亲</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ài<br />&#13;\n爱</span><span>hù<br />&#13;\n护</span><span>qī<br />&#13;\n妻</span><span>yǔ<br />&#13;\n与</span><span>zǐ<br />&#13;\n子</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>cóng<br />&#13;\n从</span><span>yè<br />&#13;\n业</span><span>yào<br />&#13;\n要</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>hài<br />&#13;\n害</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>bù<br />&#13;\n布</span><span>shī<br />&#13;\n施</span><span>hǎo<br />&#13;\n好</span><span>pǐn<br />&#13;\n品</span><span>dé<br />&#13;\n德</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>bāng<br />&#13;\n帮</span><span>zhù<br />&#13;\n助</span><span>zhòng<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>qīn<br />&#13;\n亲</span><span>juàn<br />&#13;\n眷</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>xíng<br />&#13;\n行</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>xiá<br />&#13;\n瑕</span><span>cī<br />&#13;\n疵</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>xié<br />&#13;\n邪</span><span>xíng<br />&#13;\n行</span><span>xū<br />&#13;\n须</span><span>jìn<br />&#13;\n禁</span><span>zhǐ<br />&#13;\n止</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>kè<br />&#13;\n克</span><span>jǐ<br />&#13;\n己</span><span>bù<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>yǐn<br />&#13;\n饮</span><span>jiǔ<br />&#13;\n酒</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>měi<br />&#13;\n美</span><span>dé<br />&#13;\n德</span><span>jiān<br />&#13;\n坚</span><span>bù<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>yí<br />&#13;\n移</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>gōng<br />&#13;\n恭</span><span>jìng<br />&#13;\n敬</span><span>yǔ<br />&#13;\n与</span><span>qiān<br />&#13;\n谦</span><span>ràng<br />&#13;\n让</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>zhī<br />&#13;\n知</span><span>zú<br />&#13;\n足</span><span>bìng<br />&#13;\n并</span><span>gǎn<br />&#13;\n感</span><span>ēn<br />&#13;\n恩</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>jí<br />&#13;\n及</span><span>shí<br />&#13;\n时</span><span>wén<br />&#13;\n闻</span><span>jiào<br />&#13;\n教</span><span>fǎ<br />&#13;\n法</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>rěn<br />&#13;\n忍</span><span>nài<br />&#13;\n耐</span><span>yǔ<br />&#13;\n与</span><span>shùn<br />&#13;\n顺</span><span>cóng<br />&#13;\n从</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>dé<br />&#13;\n得</span><span>jiàn<br />&#13;\n见</span><span>zhòng<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>shā<br />&#13;\n沙</span><span>mén<br />&#13;\n门</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>shì<br />&#13;\n适</span><span>shí<br />&#13;\n时</span><span>lùn<br />&#13;\n论</span><span>xìn<br />&#13;\n信</span><span>yǎng<br />&#13;\n仰</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>zì<br />&#13;\n自</span><span>zhì<br />&#13;\n制</span><span>jìng<br />&#13;\n净</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>huó<br />&#13;\n活</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>lǐng<br />&#13;\n领</span><span>wù<br />&#13;\n悟</span><span>bā<br />&#13;\n八</span><span>zhèng<br />&#13;\n正</span><span>dào<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>shí<br />&#13;\n实</span><span>zhèng<br />&#13;\n证</span><span>niè<br />&#13;\n涅</span><span>pán<br />&#13;\n槃</span><span>fǎ<br />&#13;\n法</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wè<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>bā<br />&#13;\n八</span><span>fēng<br />&#13;\n风</span><span>bù<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>dòng<br />&#13;\n动</span><span>xīn<br />&#13;\n心</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>yōu<br />&#13;\n忧</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>wū<br />&#13;\n污</span><span>rǎn<br />&#13;\n染</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>níng<br />&#13;\n宁</span><span>jìng<br />&#13;\n静</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>fán<br />&#13;\n烦</span><span>nǎo<br />&#13;\n恼</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>yī<br />&#13;\n依</span><span>cǐ<br />&#13;\n此</span><span>xíng<br />&#13;\n行</span><span>chí<br />&#13;\n持</span><span>zhě<br />&#13;\n者</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>wǎng<br />&#13;\n往</span><span>ér<br />&#13;\n而</span><span>bú<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>shèng<br />&#13;\n胜</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span></p>\n<p><span>yí<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>qiè<br />&#13;\n切</span><span>chù<br />&#13;\n处</span><span>dé<br />&#13;\n得</span><span>fú<br />&#13;\n福</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n最</span><span>jí<br />&#13;\n吉</span><span>xiáng<br />&#13;\n祥</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n</div>"
